title: #49 - Austin Show Reacts to Sykkuno Collab & Logan Paul Drama
itunes:title: #49 - Austin Show Reacts to Sykkuno Collab & Logan Paul Drama
description: You've seen him collab with CouRage, Nadeshot, BrookeAB, and Valkyrae on the 100 Thieves content house, learned a little about his rise to internet stardom on Unwrapped, and now Austin Show makes his debut appearance on The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast. Taking another in-depth look on how Love or Host became one of the most popular internet reality shows on Twitch, Austin reveals some of the craziest moments (and guests) that have never been told before to the public.
